// =============================================================================
// v_2.ino - ESP32 embedded receiver/protection prototype
//
// Based on receiver/python/v_1/v_1.ino + read_from_generator_rms_robust.py.
// The ESP32 now owns the critical path:
//   ADC -> offset/scale -> cycle detection -> Fourier phasors -> protections -> relay.
//
// Logging is intentionally decoupled from protection. The firmware keeps a compact
// circular RAM log and dumps essential CSV only when requested over Serial.
// This is the first embedded step before replacing RAM logging with SD/binary log.
// =============================================================================

